My dear, I'd turned the pony music into classic music

Hi, everypony ,here comes me Sean again, this time i present my first clarinet concerto work, and using the theme of "Winter warp up" to complete the whole music
this concerto was using the style of Mozart, and as you can hear ,this composing is very different from the other "Winter warp up orchestra version" that's because mine was totally based on the theory of classical music .

hope you enjoy it


Sean.M
